The paper proposes a method for knowledge transfer in neural networks, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The method involves distillation of activation boundaries formed by hidden neurons, which is related to the field of computer vision (cs.CV) and neural engineering (cs.NE). The proposed method also involves designing a loss function, which is a common topic in natural language processing (cs.CL). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, and cs.CL.
